Statistics code uses simplified course enrolment logic, overrides are ignored and there is a maximum number of verified parent course categories. Number 0 means detect only direct role assignments on site and course level, 1 means detect also role assignments in parent category of course, etc. Higher numbers result in much higher database server load during stats processing.
